00303         uc = s->uc + s->uc1 * T0;

00373           T2 = T1 * (1.0 + 2.0 * T1);

00700 /*--------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00701 std::string MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS8::dev_type()const
00702 {
00703   if (polarity == pN) {
00704     return "nmos8";
00705   }else if (polarity == pP) {
00706     return "pmos8";
00707   }else if (polarity == pN) {
00708     return "nmos49";
00709   }else if (polarity == pP) {
00710     return "pmos49";
00711   }else{untested();//235
00712     return MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS_BASE::dev_type();
00713   }
00714 }
00715 /*--------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00716 void MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS8::set_dev_type(const std::string& new_type)
00717 {
00718   if (Umatch(new_type, "nmos8 ")) {
00719     polarity = pN;
00720   }else if (Umatch(new_type, "pmos8 ")) {
00721     polarity = pP;
00722   }else if (Umatch(new_type, "nmos49 ")) {
00723     polarity = pN;
00724   }else if (Umatch(new_type, "pmos49 ")) {
00725     polarity = pP;
00726   }else{
00727     MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS_BASE::set_dev_type(new_type);
00728   }
00729 }
00730 /*--------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00731 void MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS8::precalc_first()
00732 {
00733     const CARD_LIST* par_scope = scope();
00734     assert(par_scope);
00735     MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS_BASE::precalc_first();
00736     e_val(&(this->capMod), 3, par_scope);
00737     e_val(&(this->nqsMod), 0, par_scope);
00738     e_val(&(this->mobMod), 1, par_scope);
00739     e_val(&(this->noiMod), 1, par_scope);
00740     e_val(&(this->paramChk), 0, par_scope);
00741     e_val(&(this->binUnit), 1, par_scope);
00742     e_val(&(this->version), 3.3, par_scope);
00743     e_val(&(this->tox), 150.0e-10, par_scope);
00744     e_val(&(this->xpart), 0.0, par_scope);
00745     e_val(&(this->jctSidewallSatCurDensity), 0.0, par_scope);
00746     e_val(&(this->mjswg), NA, par_scope);
00747     e_val(&(this->pbswg), NA, par_scope);
00748     e_val(&(this->unitLengthGateSidewallJctCap), NA, par_scope);
00749     e_val(&(this->jctEmissionCoeff), 1.0, par_scope);
00750     e_val(&(this->jctTempExponent), 3.0, par_scope);
00751     e_val(&(this->Lint), 0.0, par_scope);
00752     e_val(&(this->Ll), 0.0, par_scope);
00753     e_val(&(this->Lln), 1.0, par_scope);
00754     e_val(&(this->Lw), 0.0, par_scope);
00755     e_val(&(this->Lwn), 1.0, par_scope);
00756     e_val(&(this->Lwl), 0.0, par_scope);
00757     e_val(&(this->Wint), 0.0, par_scope);
00758     e_val(&(this->Wl), 0.0, par_scope);
00759     e_val(&(this->Wln), 1.0, par_scope);
00760     e_val(&(this->Ww), 0.0, par_scope);
00761     e_val(&(this->Wwn), 1.0, par_scope);
00762     e_val(&(this->Wwl), 0.0, par_scope);
00763     e_val(&(this->dwc), NA, par_scope);
00764     e_val(&(this->dlc), NA, par_scope);
00765     e_val(&(this->noia), NA, par_scope);
00766     e_val(&(this->noib), NA, par_scope);
00767     e_val(&(this->noic), NA, par_scope);
00768     e_val(&(this->em), 4.1e7, par_scope);
00769     e_val(&(this->ef), 1.0, par_scope);
00770     e_val(&(this->acnqsMod), 0, par_scope);
00771     e_val(&(this->toxm), tox, par_scope);
00772     e_val(&(this->lintnoi), 0.0, par_scope);
00773     e_val(&(this->ijth), 0.1, par_scope);
00774     e_val(&(this->tpb), 0.0, par_scope);
00775     e_val(&(this->tcj), 0.0, par_scope);
00776     e_val(&(this->tpbsw), 0.0, par_scope);
00777     e_val(&(this->tcjsw), 0.0, par_scope);
00778     e_val(&(this->tpbswg), 0.0, par_scope);
00779     e_val(&(this->tcjswg), 0.0, par_scope);
00780     e_val(&(this->Llc), Ll, par_scope);
00781     e_val(&(this->Lwc), Lw, par_scope);
00782     e_val(&(this->Lwlc), Lwl, par_scope);
00783     e_val(&(this->Wlc), Wl, par_scope);
00784     e_val(&(this->Wwc), Ww, par_scope);
00785     e_val(&(this->Wwlc), Wwl, par_scope);
00786     e_val(&(this->acm), 10, par_scope);
00787     // final adjust: code_pre
00788 
00789       //tox = std::max(tox, 1e-20);
00790       cox = 3.453133e-11 / tox;
00791     // final adjust: override
00792     if (mjsw == NA) {
00793       mjsw = .33;
00794     }else{
00795     }
00796     if (pb == NA) {
00797       pb = 1.0;
00798     }else{
00799     }
00800     //pb = std::max(pb, 0.1);
00801     if (pbsw == NA) {
00802       pbsw = pb;
00803     }else{
00804     }
00805     //pbsw = std::max(pbsw, 0.1);
00806     if (cgdo == NA) {
00807       cgdo = (((dlc != NA) && (dlc > 0.0))
00808           ? dlc * cox - cgdl.nom()
00809           : 0.6 * xj.nom() * cox);
00810     }else{
00811     }
00812     if (cgso == NA) {
00813       cgso = (((dlc != NA) && (dlc > 0.0))
00814           ? dlc * cox - cgsl.nom()
00815           : 0.6 * xj.nom() * cox);
00816     }else{
00817     }
00818     if (cgbo == NA) {
00819       cgbo = ((dwc != NA)
00820           ? 2.0 * dwc  * cox
00821           : 2.0 * Wint * cox);
00822     }else{
00823     }
00824     cmodel = ((!cmodel)?0:cmodel);
00825     needs_isub = (alpha0.nom()!=0.);
00826     // final adjust: raw
00827     e_val(&(this->capMod), 3, par_scope);
00828     e_val(&(this->nqsMod), 0, par_scope);
00829     e_val(&(this->mobMod), 1, par_scope);
00830     e_val(&(this->noiMod), 1, par_scope);
00831     e_val(&(this->paramChk), 0, par_scope);
00832     e_val(&(this->binUnit), 1, par_scope);
00833     e_val(&(this->version), 3.3, par_scope);
00834     e_val(&(this->tox), 150.0e-10, par_scope);
00835     e_val(&(this->xpart), 0.0, par_scope);
00836     e_val(&(this->jctSidewallSatCurDensity), 0.0, par_scope);
00837     e_val(&(this->mjswg), mjsw, par_scope);
00838     e_val(&(this->pbswg), pbsw, par_scope);
00839     //this->pbswg = std::max(pbswg, 0.1);
00840     e_val(&(this->unitLengthGateSidewallJctCap), cjsw, par_scope);
00841     e_val(&(this->jctEmissionCoeff), 1.0, par_scope);
00842     e_val(&(this->jctTempExponent), 3.0, par_scope);
00843     e_val(&(this->Lint), 0.0, par_scope);
00844     e_val(&(this->Ll), 0.0, par_scope);
00845     e_val(&(this->Lln), 1.0, par_scope);
00846     e_val(&(this->Lw), 0.0, par_scope);
00847     e_val(&(this->Lwn), 1.0, par_scope);
00848     e_val(&(this->Lwl), 0.0, par_scope);
00849     e_val(&(this->Wint), 0.0, par_scope);
00850     e_val(&(this->Wl), 0.0, par_scope);
00851     e_val(&(this->Wln), 1.0, par_scope);
00852     e_val(&(this->Ww), 0.0, par_scope);
00853     e_val(&(this->Wwn), 1.0, par_scope);
00854     e_val(&(this->Wwl), 0.0, par_scope);
00855     e_val(&(this->dwc), Wint, par_scope);
00856     e_val(&(this->dlc), Lint, par_scope);
00857     e_val(&(this->noia), (polarity==pN) ? 1e20 : 9.9e18, par_scope);
00858     e_val(&(this->noib), (polarity==pN) ? 5e4 : 2.4e3, par_scope);
00859     e_val(&(this->noic), (polarity==pN) ?-1.4e-12 :1.4e-12, par_scope);
00860     e_val(&(this->em), 4.1e7, par_scope);
00861     e_val(&(this->ef), 1.0, par_scope);
00862     e_val(&(this->acnqsMod), 0, par_scope);
00863     //this->acnqsMod = std::min(acnqsMod, 1);
00864     e_val(&(this->toxm), tox, par_scope);
00865     e_val(&(this->lintnoi), 0.0, par_scope);
00866     e_val(&(this->ijth), 0.1, par_scope);
00867     e_val(&(this->tpb), 0.0, par_scope);
00868     e_val(&(this->tcj), 0.0, par_scope);
00869     e_val(&(this->tpbsw), 0.0, par_scope);
00870     e_val(&(this->tcjsw), 0.0, par_scope);
00871     e_val(&(this->tpbswg), 0.0, par_scope);
00872     e_val(&(this->tcjswg), 0.0, par_scope);
00873     e_val(&(this->Llc), Ll, par_scope);
00874     e_val(&(this->Lwc), Lw, par_scope);
00875     e_val(&(this->Lwlc), Lwl, par_scope);
00876     e_val(&(this->Wlc), Wl, par_scope);
00877     e_val(&(this->Wwc), Ww, par_scope);
00878     e_val(&(this->Wwlc), Wwl, par_scope);
00879     e_val(&(this->acm), 10, par_scope);
00880     // final adjust: mid
00881     // final adjust: calculated
00882     factor1 = sqrt(tox * P_EPS_SI / P_EPS_OX);
00883     vt_at_tnom = tnom_k * P_K_Q;
00884     ni = (1.45e10 * (tnom_k / 300.15)
00885          * sqrt(tnom_k / 300.15)
00886          * exp(21.5565981 - egap / (2.0 * vt_at_tnom)));
00887     // final adjust: post
00888 
00889       if (npeak.nom() > 1.0e20) {
00890         npeak.set_nom(npeak.nom() * 1.0e-6);
00891       }
00892       if (ngate.nom() > 1.0e23) {
00893         ngate.set_nom(ngate.nom() * 1.0e-6);
00894       }
00895     // final adjust: done
00896 }

00900     MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS_BASE::precalc_last();
00901 }
00902 /*--------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
00903 SDP_CARD* MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS8::new_sdp(COMMON_COMPONENT* c)const
00904 {
00905   assert(c);
00906   if (COMMON_BUILT_IN_MOS* cc = dynamic_cast<COMMON_BUILT_IN_MOS*>(c)) {
00907     if (cc->_sdp) {
00908       cc->_sdp->init(cc);
00909       return cc->_sdp;
00910     }else{
00911       delete cc->_sdp;
00912       return new SDP_BUILT_IN_MOS8(c);
00913     }
00914   }else{
00915     return MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS_BASE::new_sdp(c);
00916   }
00917 }

02931 /*--------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
02932 bool MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS8::is_valid(const COMPONENT* d)const
02933 {
02934   assert(d);
02935   return MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS_BASE::is_valid(d);
02936 }
02937 /*--------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
02938 void MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS8::tr_eval(COMPONENT* brh)const
02939 {
02940   DEV_BUILT_IN_MOS* d = prechecked_cast<DEV_BUILT_IN_MOS*>(brh);
02941   assert(d);
02942   const COMMON_BUILT_IN_MOS* c = prechecked_cast<const COMMON_BUILT_IN_MOS*>(d->common());
02943   assert(c);
02944   const SDP_BUILT_IN_MOS8* s = prechecked_cast<const SDP_BUILT_IN_MOS8*>(c->sdp());
02945   assert(s);
02946   const MODEL_BUILT_IN_MOS8* m = this;
02947   const TDP_BUILT_IN_MOS8 T(d);
02948   const TDP_BUILT_IN_MOS8* t = &T;
02949 
02950     trace3("", d->vds, d->vgs, d->vbs);
02951     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
02952     const double EXP_THRESHOLD = 34.0;
02953     const double MIN_EXP = 1.713908431e-15;
02954     const double MAX_EXP = 5.834617425e14;
02955     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
02956     d->reverse_if_needed();
02957     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
02958     double Vbseff, dVbseff_dVb;
02959     {
02960       double T0 = d->vbs - t->vbsc - 0.001;
02961       double T1 = sqrt(T0 * T0 - 0.004 * t->vbsc);
02962       trace3("", t->vbsc, T0, T1);
02963       Vbseff = t->vbsc + 0.5 * (T0 + T1);
02964       dVbseff_dVb = 0.5 * (1.0 + T0 / T1);
02965       trace2("raw", Vbseff, dVbseff_dVb);
02966 
02967       fixzero(&Vbseff, t->vbsc);
02968       if (Vbseff < d->vbs) {    // From Spice, to fix numeric problems
02969         //untested();           // inadequately.  Above fixzero should do a 
02970         Vbseff = d->vbs;        // better job, but I left this in case.
02971       }
02972     }
02973     trace2("fixed", Vbseff, dVbseff_dVb);
02974     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
02975     double Phis, dPhis_dVb, sqrtPhis, dsqrtPhis_dVb;
02976     if (Vbseff > 0.0) {
02977         //untested();
02978       d->sbfwd = true;
02979       double T0 = t->phi / (t->phi + Vbseff);
02980       Phis = t->phi * T0;
02981       dPhis_dVb = -T0 * T0;
02982       sqrtPhis = t->phis3 / (t->phi + 0.5 * Vbseff);
02983       dsqrtPhis_dVb = -0.5 * sqrtPhis * sqrtPhis / t->phis3;
02984       trace0("bs-fwd-bias");
02985     }else{
02986       d->sbfwd = false;
02987       Phis = t->phi - Vbseff;
02988       dPhis_dVb = -1.0;
02989       sqrtPhis = sqrt(Phis);
02990       dsqrtPhis_dVb = -0.5 / sqrtPhis;
02991       trace0("bs-normal");
02992     }
02993     trace4("", Phis, dPhis_dVb, sqrtPhis, dsqrtPhis_dVb);
02994     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
02995     double Xdep = t->Xdep0 * sqrtPhis / t->sqrtPhi;
02996     double dXdep_dVb = (t->Xdep0 / t->sqrtPhi) * dsqrtPhis_dVb;
02997     trace2("", Xdep, dXdep_dVb);
02998     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
02999     double Theta0, dTheta0_dVb;
03000     {
03001       double lt1, dlt1_dVb;
03002       {
03003         double T3 = sqrt(Xdep);
03004         double T0 = s->dvt2 * Vbseff;
03005         double T1, T2;
03006         if (T0 >= - 0.5) {
03007           T1 = 1.0 + T0;
03008           T2 = s->dvt2;
03009           trace4("", T0, T1, T2, T3);
03010         }else{
03011           untested();
03012           /* Added to avoid any discontinuity problems caused by dvt2 */ 
03013           double T4 = 1.0 / (3.0 + 8.0 * T0);
03014           T1 = (1.0 + 3.0 * T0) * T4; 
03015           T2 = s->dvt2 * T4 * T4;
03016           trace4("dvd2 fix", T0, T1, T2, T3);
03017         }
03018         lt1 = m->factor1 * T3 * T1;
03019         dlt1_dVb = m->factor1 * (0.5 / T3 * T1 * dXdep_dVb + T3 * T2);
03020       }
03021       trace2("", lt1, dlt1_dVb);
03022 
03023       double T0 = -0.5 * s->dvt1 * s->leff / lt1;
03024       if (T0 > -EXP_THRESHOLD) {
03025         double T1 = exp(T0);
03026         Theta0 = T1 * (1.0 + 2.0 * T1);
03027         double dT1_dVb = -T0 / lt1 * T1 * dlt1_dVb;
03028         dTheta0_dVb = (1.0 + 4.0 * T1) * dT1_dVb;
03029         trace2("T0 > -ET", Theta0, dTheta0_dVb);
03030       }else{
03031         double T1 = MIN_EXP;
03032         Theta0 = T1 * (1.0 + 2.0 * T1);
03033         dTheta0_dVb = 0.0;
03034         trace2("T0 < -ET", Theta0, dTheta0_dVb);
03035       }
03036     }
03037     trace2("", Theta0, dTheta0_dVb);
03038     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03039     double dVth_dVb, dVth_dVd; // d->von
03040     {
03041       double V0 = t->vbi - t->phi;
03042       double T2, dT2_dVb;
03043       {
03044         double ltw, dltw_dVb;
03045         {
03046           double T3 = sqrt(Xdep);
03047           double T0 = s->dvt2w * Vbseff;
03048           double T1, t2;
03049           if (T0 >= - 0.5) {
03050             T1 = 1.0 + T0;
03051             t2 = s->dvt2w;
03052           }else{
03053             untested();
03054             /* Added to avoid any discontinuity problems caused by dvt2w */ 
03055             double T4 = 1.0 / (3.0 + 8.0 * T0);
03056             T1 = (1.0 + 3.0 * T0) * T4; 
03057             t2 = s->dvt2w * T4 * T4;
03058           }
03059           trace4("", T0, T1, t2, T3);
03060           ltw = m->factor1 * T3 * T1;
03061           dltw_dVb = m->factor1 * (0.5 / T3 * T1 * dXdep_dVb + T3 * t2);
03062         }
03063         trace2("", ltw, dltw_dVb);
03064         double T0 = -0.5 * s->dvt1w * s->weff * s->leff / ltw;
03065         if (T0 > -EXP_THRESHOLD) {
03066           double T1 = exp(T0);
03067           T2 = T1 * (1.0 + 2.0 * T1);
03068           double dT1_dVb = -T0 / ltw * T1 * dltw_dVb;
03069           dT2_dVb = (1.0 + 4.0 * T1) * dT1_dVb;
03070         }else{
03071           double T1 = MIN_EXP;
03072           T2 = T1 * (1.0 + 2.0 * T1);
03073           dT2_dVb = 0.0;
03074         }
03075         T0 = s->dvt0w * T2;
03076         T2 = T0 * V0;
03077         dT2_dVb = s->dvt0w * dT2_dVb * V0;
03078       }
03079       trace3("", V0, T2, dT2_dVb);
03080       double T0 = sqrt(1.0 + s->nlx / s->leff);
03081       double T1 = t->k1ox * (T0 - 1.0) * t->sqrtPhi
03082         + (s->kt1 + s->kt1l / s->leff + s->kt2 * Vbseff) * t->tempratio_1;
03083       double tmp2 = m->tox * t->phi / (s->weff + s->w0);
03084       
03085       double T3 = s->eta0 + s->etab * Vbseff;
03086       trace4("", T0, T1, tmp2, T3);
03087       double T4;
03088       if (T3 < 1.0e-4) {
03089         untested();
03090         /* avoid  discontinuity problems caused by etab */ 
03091         double T9 = 1.0 / (3.0 - 2.0e4 * T3);
03092         T3 = (2.0e-4 - T3) * T9;
03093         T4 = T9 * T9;
03094         trace3("", T9, T3, T4);
03095       }else{
03096         T4 = 1.0;
03097         trace1("", T4);
03098       }
03099       double thetavth = s->dvt0 * Theta0;
03100       double Delt_vth = thetavth * V0;
03101       double dDelt_vth_dVb = s->dvt0 * dTheta0_dVb * V0;
03102       trace4("", thetavth, t->theta0vb0, Delt_vth, dDelt_vth_dVb);
03103       double dDIBL_Sft_dVd = T3 * t->theta0vb0;
03104       double DIBL_Sft = dDIBL_Sft_dVd * d->vds;
03105       trace2("", dDIBL_Sft_dVd, DIBL_Sft);
03106       
03107       trace4("", t->vth0, t->k1, sqrtPhis, t->sqrtPhi);
03108       trace4("", t->k2, Vbseff, Delt_vth, T2);
03109       trace4("", s->k3, s->k3b, Vbseff, tmp2);
03110       trace2("", T1, DIBL_Sft);
03111       double Vth = m->polarity * t->vth0 + t->k1ox * sqrtPhis 
03112         - t->k1 *  t->sqrtPhi - t->k2ox * Vbseff - Delt_vth - T2
03113         + (s->k3 + s->k3b * Vbseff) * tmp2 + T1 - DIBL_Sft;
03114       d->von = Vth;
03115       
03116       dVth_dVb = t->k1ox * dsqrtPhis_dVb - t->k2ox  - dDelt_vth_dVb - dT2_dVb
03117         + s->k3b * tmp2 - s->etab * d->vds * t->theta0vb0 * T4
03118         + s->kt2 * t->tempratio_1;
03119       dVth_dVd = -dDIBL_Sft_dVd; 
03120     }
03121     trace3("", d->von, dVth_dVb, dVth_dVd);
03122     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03123     /* Calculate n */
03124     double n, dn_dVb, dn_dVd;
03125     {
03126       double tmp2 = s->nfactor * P_EPS_SI / Xdep;
03127       double tmp3 = s->cdsc + s->cdscb * Vbseff + s->cdscd * d->vds;
03128       double tmp4 = (tmp2 + tmp3 * Theta0 + s->cit) / m->cox;
03129       trace3("", tmp2, tmp3, tmp4);
03130       if (tmp4 >= -0.5) {
03131         n = 1.0 + tmp4;
03132         dn_dVb = (-tmp2 / Xdep * dXdep_dVb + tmp3 * dTheta0_dVb 
03133                   + s->cdscb * Theta0) / m->cox;
03134         dn_dVd = s->cdscd * Theta0 / m->cox;
03135         trace3("n", n, dn_dVb, dn_dVd);
03136       }else{
03137         /* avoid  discontinuity problems caused by tmp4 */ 
03138         double T0 = 1.0 / (3.0 + 8.0 * tmp4);
03139         n = (1.0 + 3.0 * tmp4) * T0;
03140         T0 *= T0;
03141         dn_dVb = (-tmp2 / Xdep * dXdep_dVb + tmp3 * dTheta0_dVb
03142                   + s->cdscb * Theta0) / m->cox * T0;
03143         dn_dVd = s->cdscd * Theta0 / m->cox * T0;
03144         trace3("n disc", n, dn_dVb, dn_dVd);
03145       }
03146     }
03147     trace3("", n, dn_dVb, dn_dVd);
03148     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03149     /* Poly Gate Si Depletion Effect */
03150     double Vgs_eff, dVgs_eff_dVg;
03151     {
03152       double T0 = t->vfb + t->phi;
03153       trace2("Poly", t->vfb, t->phi);
03154       trace3("", s->ngate, d->vgs, T0);
03155       if ((s->ngate > 1.e18) && (s->ngate < 1.e25) && (d->vgs > T0)) {
03156         /* added to avoid the problem caused by ngate */
03157         double T1 = 1.0e6 * P_Q * P_EPS_SI * s->ngate / (m->cox * m->cox);
03158         double T4 = sqrt(1.0 + 2.0 * (d->vgs - T0) / T1);
03159         double T2 = T1 * (T4 - 1.0);
03160         double T3 = 0.5 * T2 * T2 / T1; /* T3 = Vpoly */
03161         double T7 = 1.12 - T3 - 0.05;
03162         double T6 = sqrt(T7 * T7 + 0.224);
03163         double T5 = 1.12 - 0.5 * (T7 + T6);
03164         Vgs_eff = d->vgs - T5;
03165         dVgs_eff_dVg = 1.0 - (0.5 - 0.5 / T4) * (1.0 + T7 / T6);
03166         trace2("><", Vgs_eff, dVgs_eff_dVg);
03167       }else{
03168         Vgs_eff = d->vgs;
03169         dVgs_eff_dVg = 1.0;
03170         trace2("const", Vgs_eff, dVgs_eff_dVg);
03171       }
03172     }
03173     trace2("", Vgs_eff, dVgs_eff_dVg);
03174     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03175     /* Effective Vgst (Vgsteff) Calculation */
03176     double /*Vgsteff,*/ dVgsteff_dVg, dVgsteff_dVd, dVgsteff_dVb, Vgst2Vtm;
03177     // d->vgst
03178     {
03179       double Vgst = Vgs_eff - d->von;
03180       double T10 = 2.0 * n * t->vtm;
03181       double VgstNVt = Vgst / T10;
03182       double ExpArg = (2.0 * s->voff - Vgst) / T10;
03183       trace4("", Vgst, T10, VgstNVt, ExpArg);
03184 
03185       /* MCJ: Very small Vgst */
03186       if (VgstNVt > EXP_THRESHOLD) {
03187         d->vgst = Vgst;
03188         dVgsteff_dVg = dVgs_eff_dVg;
03189         dVgsteff_dVd = -dVth_dVd;
03190         dVgsteff_dVb = -dVth_dVb;
03191         trace4(">>", d->vgst, dVgsteff_dVg, dVgsteff_dVd, dVgsteff_dVb);
03192       }else if (ExpArg > EXP_THRESHOLD) {
03193         double T0 = (Vgst - s->voff) / (n * t->vtm);
03194         double ExpVgst = exp(T0);
03195         d->vgst = t->vtm * t->cdep0 / m->cox * ExpVgst;
03196         dVgsteff_dVg = d->vgst / (n * t->vtm);
03197         dVgsteff_dVd = -dVgsteff_dVg * (dVth_dVd + T0 * t->vtm * dn_dVd);
03198         dVgsteff_dVb = -dVgsteff_dVg * (dVth_dVb + T0 * t->vtm * dn_dVb);
03199         dVgsteff_dVg *= dVgs_eff_dVg;
03200         trace4(">", d->vgst, dVgsteff_dVg, dVgsteff_dVd, dVgsteff_dVb);
03201       }else{
03202         double ExpVgst = exp(VgstNVt);
03203         double T1 = T10 * log(1.0 + ExpVgst);
03204         double dT1_dVg = ExpVgst / (1.0 + ExpVgst);
03205         double dT1_dVb = -dT1_dVg * (dVth_dVb + Vgst / n * dn_dVb)
03206                       + T1 / n * dn_dVb; 
03207         double dT1_dVd = -dT1_dVg * (dVth_dVd + Vgst / n * dn_dVd)
03208                       + T1 / n * dn_dVd;
03209 
03210         double dT2_dVg = -m->cox / (t->vtm * t->cdep0)
03211                       * exp(ExpArg);
03212         double T2 = 1.0 - T10 * dT2_dVg;
03213         double dT2_dVd = -dT2_dVg * (dVth_dVd - 2.0 * t->vtm * ExpArg * dn_dVd)
03214                       + (T2 - 1.0) / n * dn_dVd;
03215         double dT2_dVb = -dT2_dVg * (dVth_dVb - 2.0 * t->vtm * ExpArg * dn_dVb)
03216                       + (T2 - 1.0) / n * dn_dVb;
03217 
03218         d->vgst = T1 / T2;
03219         double T3 = T2 * T2;
03220         dVgsteff_dVg = (T2 * dT1_dVg - T1 * dT2_dVg) / T3 * dVgs_eff_dVg;
03221         dVgsteff_dVd = (T2 * dT1_dVd - T1 * dT2_dVd) / T3;
03222         dVgsteff_dVb = (T2 * dT1_dVb - T1 * dT2_dVb) / T3;
03223         trace4("<", d->vgst, dVgsteff_dVg, dVgsteff_dVd, dVgsteff_dVb);
03224       }
03225       Vgst2Vtm = d->vgst + 2.0 * t->vtm;
03226       trace3("", d->vgst, t->vtm, Vgst2Vtm);
03227     }
03228     trace1("", d->vgst);
03229     trace4("", dVgsteff_dVg, dVgsteff_dVd, dVgsteff_dVb, Vgst2Vtm);
03230     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03231     /* Calculate Effective Channel Geometry */
03232     double Weff, dWeff_dVg, dWeff_dVb;
03233     {
03234       double T9 = sqrtPhis - t->sqrtPhi;
03235       Weff = s->weff - 2.0 * (s->dwg * d->vgst + s->dwb * T9); 
03236       dWeff_dVg = -2.0 * s->dwg;
03237       dWeff_dVb = -2.0 * s->dwb * dsqrtPhis_dVb;
03238 
03239       if (Weff < 2.0e-8) {
03240         /* to avoid the discontinuity problem due to Weff*/
03241         double T0 = 1.0 / (6.0e-8 - 2.0 * Weff);
03242         Weff = 2.0e-8 * (4.0e-8 - Weff) * T0;
03243         T0 *= T0 * 4.0e-16;
03244         dWeff_dVg *= T0;
03245         dWeff_dVb *= T0;
03246         trace3("Weff fix", Weff, dWeff_dVg, dWeff_dVb);
03247       }
03248     }
03249     trace3("", Weff, dWeff_dVg, dWeff_dVb);
03250     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03251     double Rds, dRds_dVg, dRds_dVb;
03252     {
03253       double T9 = sqrtPhis - t->sqrtPhi;
03254       double T0 = s->prwg * d->vgst + s->prwb * T9;
03255       if (T0 >= -0.9) {
03256         Rds = t->rds0 * (1.0 + T0);
03257         dRds_dVg = t->rds0 * s->prwg;
03258         dRds_dVb = t->rds0 * s->prwb * dsqrtPhis_dVb;
03259       }else{
03260         /* to avoid the discontinuity problem due to prwg and prwb*/
03261         double T1 = 1.0 / (17.0 + 20.0 * T0);
03262         Rds = t->rds0 * (0.8 + T0) * T1;
03263         T1 *= T1;
03264         dRds_dVg = t->rds0 * s->prwg * T1;
03265         dRds_dVb = t->rds0 * s->prwb * dsqrtPhis_dVb * T1;
03266         trace3("Rds fix", T9, T0, T1);
03267         trace3("Rds fix", Rds, dRds_dVg, dRds_dVb);
03268       }
03270     }
03271     trace3("", Rds, dRds_dVg, dRds_dVb);
03272     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03273     /* Calculate Abulk */
03274     double Abulk0, dAbulk0_dVb, dAbulk_dVg, Abulk, dAbulk_dVb;
03275     {
03276       double T1 = 0.5 * t->k1ox / sqrtPhis;
03277       double dT1_dVb = -T1 / sqrtPhis * dsqrtPhis_dVb;
03278 
03279       double T9 = sqrt(s->xj * Xdep);
03280       double tmp1 = s->leff + 2.0 * T9;
03281       double T5 = s->leff / tmp1; 
03282       double tmp2 = s->a0 * T5;
03283       double tmp3 = s->weff + s->b1; 
03284       double tmp4 = s->b0 / tmp3;
03285       double T2 = tmp2 + tmp4;
03286       double dT2_dVb = -T9 / tmp1 / Xdep * dXdep_dVb;
03287       double T6 = T5 * T5;
03288       double T7 = T5 * T6;
03289 
03290       Abulk0 = 1.0 + T1 * T2; 
03291       dAbulk0_dVb = T1 * tmp2 * dT2_dVb + T2 * dT1_dVb;
03292 
03293       double T8 = s->ags * s->a0 * T7;
03294       dAbulk_dVg = -T1 * T8;
03295       Abulk = Abulk0 + dAbulk_dVg * d->vgst; 
03296       dAbulk_dVb = dAbulk0_dVb - T8 * d->vgst * (dT1_dVb + 3.0 * T1 * dT2_dVb);
03297 
03298       trace2("1", Abulk0, dAbulk0_dVb);
03299       trace3("1", dAbulk_dVg, Abulk, dAbulk_dVb);
03300 
03301       if (Abulk0 < 0.1) {
03302         /* added to avoid the problems caused by Abulk0 */
03303         double t9 = 1.0 / (3.0 - 20.0 * Abulk0);
03304         Abulk0 = (0.2 - Abulk0) * t9;
03305         dAbulk0_dVb *= t9 * t9;
03306         trace2("2", Abulk0, dAbulk0_dVb);
03307       }
03308       if (Abulk < 0.1) {
03309         /* added to avoid the problems caused by Abulk */
03310         double t9 = 1.0 / (3.0 - 20.0 * Abulk);
03311         Abulk = (0.2 - Abulk) * t9;
03312         double T10 = t9 * t9;
03313         dAbulk_dVb *= T10;
03314         dAbulk_dVg *= T10;
03315         trace3("2", dAbulk_dVg, Abulk, dAbulk_dVb);
03316       }
03318 
03319       double T0, dT0_dVb;
03320       {
03321         double t2 = s->keta * Vbseff;
03322         if (t2 >= -0.9) {
03323           T0 = 1.0 / (1.0 + t2);
03324           dT0_dVb = -s->keta * T0 * T0;
03325           trace3("", t2, T0, dT0_dVb);
03326         }else{
03327           /* added to avoid the problems caused by Keta */
03328           double t1 = 1.0 / (0.8 + t2);
03329           T0 = (17.0 + 20.0 * t2) * t1;
03330           dT0_dVb = -s->keta * t1 * t1;
03331           trace3("keta fix", t2, T0, dT0_dVb);
03332         }
03333       }
03334       dAbulk_dVg *= T0;
03335       dAbulk_dVb = dAbulk_dVb * T0 + Abulk * dT0_dVb;
03336       dAbulk0_dVb = dAbulk0_dVb * T0 + Abulk0 * dT0_dVb;
03337       Abulk *= T0;
03338       Abulk0 *= T0;
03340     }
03341     trace2("", Abulk0, dAbulk0_dVb);
03342     trace3("", dAbulk_dVg, Abulk, dAbulk_dVb);
03343     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03344     /* Mobility calculation */
03345     double ueff, dueff_dVg, dueff_dVd, dueff_dVb;
03346     {
03347       double Denomi, dDenomi_dVg, dDenomi_dVd, dDenomi_dVb;
03348       {
03349         double T5;
03350         if (m->mobMod == 1) {
03351           double T0 = d->vgst + d->von + d->von;
03352           double T2 = t->ua + t->uc * Vbseff;
03353           double T3 = T0 / m->tox;
03354           T5 = T3 * (T2 + t->ub * T3);
03355           dDenomi_dVg = (T2 + 2.0 * t->ub * T3) / m->tox;
03356           dDenomi_dVd = dDenomi_dVg * 2.0 * dVth_dVd;
03357           dDenomi_dVb = dDenomi_dVg * 2.0 * dVth_dVb + t->uc * T3;
03358         }else if (m->mobMod == 2) {
03359           T5 = d->vgst / m->tox 
03360             * (t->ua + t->uc * Vbseff + t->ub * d->vgst / m->tox);
03361           dDenomi_dVg = (t->ua + t->uc * Vbseff + 2.0 * t->ub * d->vgst / m->tox)
03362             / m->tox;
03363           dDenomi_dVd = 0.0;
03364           dDenomi_dVb = d->vgst * t->uc / m->tox; 
03365         }else{
03366           double T0 = d->vgst + d->von + d->von;
03367           double T2 = 1.0 + t->uc * Vbseff;
03368           double T3 = T0 / m->tox;
03369           double T4 = T3 * (t->ua + t->ub * T3);
03370           T5 = T4 * T2;
03371           dDenomi_dVg = (t->ua + 2.0 * t->ub * T3) * T2 / m->tox;
03372           dDenomi_dVd = dDenomi_dVg * 2.0 * dVth_dVd;
03373           dDenomi_dVb = dDenomi_dVg * 2.0 * dVth_dVb + t->uc * T4;
03374         }
03375         if (T5 >= -0.8) {
03376           Denomi = 1.0 + T5;
03377         }else{
03378           /* Added to avoid the discontinuity problem caused by ua and ub*/ 
03379           double T9 = 1.0 / (7.0 + 10.0 * T5);
03380           Denomi = (0.6 + T5) * T9;
03381           T9 *= T9;
03382           dDenomi_dVg *= T9;
03383           dDenomi_dVd *= T9;
03384           dDenomi_dVb *= T9;
03385         }
03386       }
03387       ueff = t->u0temp / Denomi;
03388       double T9 = -ueff / Denomi;
03389       dueff_dVg = T9 * dDenomi_dVg;
03390       dueff_dVd = T9 * dDenomi_dVd;
03391       dueff_dVb = T9 * dDenomi_dVb;
03392     }
03393     trace4("", ueff, dueff_dVg, dueff_dVd, dueff_dVb);
03394     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03395     double Esat, EsatL, dEsatL_dVg, dEsatL_dVd, dEsatL_dVb;
03396     {
03397       Esat = 2.0 * t->vsattemp / ueff;
03398       EsatL = Esat * s->leff;
03399       double T0 = -EsatL /ueff;
03400       dEsatL_dVg = T0 * dueff_dVg;
03401       dEsatL_dVd = T0 * dueff_dVd;
03402       dEsatL_dVb = T0 * dueff_dVb;
03403     }
03404     trace2("", Esat, EsatL);
03405     trace3("", dEsatL_dVg, dEsatL_dVd, dEsatL_dVb);
03406     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03407     /* Saturation Drain Voltage Vdsat */
03408     double Vdsat, dVdsat_dVg, dVdsat_dVd, dVdsat_dVb; // d->vdsat
03409     double Vasat, dVasat_dVg, dVasat_dVb, dVasat_dVd;
03410     {
03411       double WVCoxRds;
03412       {
03413         double WVCox = Weff * t->vsattemp * m->cox;
03414         WVCoxRds = WVCox * Rds;
03415       }
03416       trace1("", WVCoxRds);
03417 
03418       double Lambda, dLambda_dVg;
03419       {
03420         if (s->a1 == 0.0) {
03421           Lambda = s->a2;
03422           dLambda_dVg = 0.0;
03423         }else if (s->a1 > 0.0) {
03424           /* avoid discontinuity problem caused by s->a1 and s->a2 (Lambda) */
03425           double T0 = 1.0 - s->a2;
03426           double T1 = T0 - s->a1 * d->vgst - 0.0001;
03427           double T2 = sqrt(T1 * T1 + 0.0004 * T0);
03428           Lambda = s->a2 + T0 - 0.5 * (T1 + T2);
03429           dLambda_dVg = 0.5 * s->a1 * (1.0 + T1 / T2);
03430         }else{
03431           double T1 = s->a2 + s->a1 * d->vgst - 0.0001;
03432           double T2 = sqrt(T1 * T1 + 0.0004 * s->a2);
03433           Lambda = 0.5 * (T1 + T2);
03434           dLambda_dVg = 0.5 * s->a1 * (1.0 + T1 / T2);
03435         }
03436       }
03437       trace2("", Lambda, dLambda_dVg);
03438 
03439       double tmp2, tmp3;
03440       if (Rds > 0) {
03441         tmp2 = dRds_dVg / Rds + dWeff_dVg / Weff;
03442         tmp3 = dRds_dVb / Rds + dWeff_dVb / Weff;
03443       }else{
03444         tmp2 = dWeff_dVg / Weff;
03445         tmp3 = dWeff_dVb / Weff;
03446       }
03447       trace2("", tmp2, tmp3);
03448 
03449       //double Vdsat, dVdsat_dVg, dVdsat_dVd, dVdsat_dVb; // d->vdsat
03450       double tmp1;
03451       {
03452         if ((Rds == 0.0) && (Lambda == 1.0)) {
03453           double T0 = 1.0 / (Abulk * EsatL + Vgst2Vtm);
03454           tmp1 = 0.0;
03455           double T1 = T0 * T0;
03456           double T2 = Vgst2Vtm * T0;
03457           double T3 = EsatL * Vgst2Vtm;
03458           Vdsat = T3 * T0;
03459           double dT0_dVg = -(Abulk * dEsatL_dVg + EsatL * dAbulk_dVg + 1.0)*T1;
03460           double dT0_dVd = -(Abulk * dEsatL_dVd) * T1; 
03461           double dT0_dVb = -(Abulk * dEsatL_dVb + dAbulk_dVb * EsatL) * T1;   
03462           dVdsat_dVg = T3 * dT0_dVg + T2 * dEsatL_dVg + EsatL * T0;
03463           dVdsat_dVd = T3 * dT0_dVd + T2 * dEsatL_dVd;
03464           dVdsat_dVb = T3 * dT0_dVb + T2 * dEsatL_dVb;   
03465         }else{
03466           tmp1 = dLambda_dVg / (Lambda * Lambda);
03467           double T9 = Abulk * WVCoxRds;
03468           double T8 = Abulk * T9;
03469           double T7 = Vgst2Vtm * T9;
03470           double T6 = Vgst2Vtm * WVCoxRds;
03471           double T0 = 2.0 * Abulk * (T9 - 1.0 + 1.0 / Lambda); 
03472           double dT0_dVg = 2.0 * (T8 * tmp2 - Abulk * tmp1
03473                         + (2.0 * T9 + 1.0 / Lambda - 1.0) * dAbulk_dVg);
03474           double dT0_dVb = 2.0 * (T8 * (2.0 / Abulk * dAbulk_dVb + tmp3)
03475                                   + (1.0 / Lambda - 1.0) * dAbulk_dVb);
03476           //double dT0_dVd = 0.0;
03477           
03478           double T1 = Vgst2Vtm * (2.0 / Lambda - 1.0) + Abulk * EsatL + 3.0*T7;
03479           double dT1_dVg = (2.0 / Lambda - 1.0) - 2.0 * Vgst2Vtm * tmp1
03480             + Abulk * dEsatL_dVg + EsatL * dAbulk_dVg 
03481             + 3.0 * (T9 + T7 * tmp2 + T6 * dAbulk_dVg);
03482           double dT1_dVb = Abulk * dEsatL_dVb + EsatL * dAbulk_dVb
03483             + 3.0 * (T6 * dAbulk_dVb + T7 * tmp3);
03484           double dT1_dVd = Abulk * dEsatL_dVd;
03485           
03486           double T2 = Vgst2Vtm * (EsatL + 2.0 * T6);
03487           double dT2_dVg = EsatL + Vgst2Vtm * dEsatL_dVg
03488             + T6 * (4.0 + 2.0 * Vgst2Vtm * tmp2);
03489           double dT2_dVb = Vgst2Vtm * (dEsatL_dVb + 2.0 * T6 * tmp3);
03490           double dT2_dVd = Vgst2Vtm * dEsatL_dVd;
03491           
03492           double T3 = sqrt(T1 * T1 - 2.0 * T0 * T2);
03493           Vdsat = (T1 - T3) / T0;
03494           dVdsat_dVg = (dT1_dVg - (T1 * dT1_dVg - dT0_dVg * T2
03495                                 - T0 * dT2_dVg) / T3 - Vdsat * dT0_dVg) / T0;
03496           dVdsat_dVb = (dT1_dVb - (T1 * dT1_dVb - dT0_dVb * T2
03497                                 - T0 * dT2_dVb) / T3 - Vdsat * dT0_dVb) / T0;
03498           dVdsat_dVd = (dT1_dVd - (T1 * dT1_dVd - T0 * dT2_dVd) / T3) / T0;
03499         }
03500         d->vdsat = Vdsat;
03501         d->saturated = (d->vds >= d->vdsat);
03502       }
03503       trace1("", tmp1);
03504       trace4("d->vdsat", Vdsat, dVdsat_dVg, dVdsat_dVd, dVdsat_dVb);
03505 
03506       /* Calculate VAsat */
03507       // double Vasat, dVasat_dVg, dVasat_dVb, dVasat_dVd;
03508       {
03509         double tmp4 = 1.0 - 0.5 * Abulk * Vdsat / Vgst2Vtm;
03510         double T9 = WVCoxRds * d->vgst;
03511         double T8 = T9 / Vgst2Vtm;
03512         double T0 = EsatL + Vdsat + 2.0 * T9 * tmp4;
03513         double T7 = 2.0 * WVCoxRds * tmp4;
03514         double dT0_dVg = dEsatL_dVg + dVdsat_dVg + T7 * (1.0 + tmp2 * d->vgst)
03515           - T8 * (Abulk * dVdsat_dVg - Abulk * Vdsat / Vgst2Vtm
03516                   + Vdsat * dAbulk_dVg);   
03517         double dT0_dVb = dEsatL_dVb + dVdsat_dVb + T7 * tmp3 * d->vgst
03518           - T8 * (dAbulk_dVb * Vdsat + Abulk * dVdsat_dVb);
03519         double dT0_dVd = dEsatL_dVd + dVdsat_dVd - T8 * Abulk * dVdsat_dVd;
03520         T9 = WVCoxRds * Abulk; 
03521         double T1 = 2.0 / Lambda - 1.0 + T9; 
03522         double dT1_dVg = -2.0 * tmp1 +  WVCoxRds * (Abulk * tmp2 + dAbulk_dVg);
03523         double dT1_dVb = dAbulk_dVb * WVCoxRds + T9 * tmp3;
03524         Vasat = T0 / T1;
03525         dVasat_dVg = (dT0_dVg - Vasat * dT1_dVg) / T1;
03526         dVasat_dVb = (dT0_dVb - Vasat * dT1_dVb) / T1;
03527         dVasat_dVd = dT0_dVd / T1;
03528       }
03529       trace4("", Vasat, dVasat_dVg, dVasat_dVb, dVasat_dVd);
03530     }
03531     trace1("", d->vdsat);
03532     trace4("", Vdsat, dVdsat_dVg, dVdsat_dVd, dVdsat_dVb);
03533     trace4("", Vasat, dVasat_dVg, dVasat_dVb, dVasat_dVd);
03534     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03535     /* Effective Vds (Vdseff) Calculation */
03536     double Vdseff, diffVds, dVdseff_dVg, dVdseff_dVd, dVdseff_dVb;
03537     {
03538       double T1 = Vdsat - d->vds - s->delta;
03539       double dT1_dVg = dVdsat_dVg;
03540       double dT1_dVd = dVdsat_dVd - 1.0;
03541       double dT1_dVb = dVdsat_dVb;
03542       trace4("", T1, dT1_dVg, dT1_dVd, dT1_dVb);
03543       
03544       double T2 = sqrt(T1 * T1 + 4.0 * s->delta * Vdsat);
03545       double T0 = T1 / T2;
03546       double T3 = 2.0 * s->delta / T2;
03547       trace3("", T2, T0, T3);
03548       double dT2_dVg = T0 * dT1_dVg + T3 * dVdsat_dVg;
03549       double dT2_dVd = T0 * dT1_dVd + T3 * dVdsat_dVd;
03550       double dT2_dVb = T0 * dT1_dVb + T3 * dVdsat_dVb;
03551       trace3("", dT2_dVg, dT2_dVd, dT2_dVb);
03552       
03553       Vdseff      = Vdsat - 0.5 * (T1 + T2);
03554       dVdseff_dVg = dVdsat_dVg - 0.5 * (dT1_dVg + dT2_dVg); 
03555       dVdseff_dVd = dVdsat_dVd - 0.5 * (dT1_dVd + dT2_dVd); 
03556       dVdseff_dVb = dVdsat_dVb - 0.5 * (dT1_dVb + dT2_dVb); 
03557       trace4("raw", Vdseff, dVdseff_dVg, dVdseff_dVd, dVdseff_dVb);
03558 
03559       fixzero(&Vdseff,      Vdsat);
03560       fixzero(&dVdseff_dVg, dVdsat_dVg);
03561       fixzero(&dVdseff_dVd, dVdsat_dVd);
03562       fixzero(&dVdseff_dVb, dVdsat_dVb);
03563       /* Added to eliminate non-zero Vdseff at Vds=0.0 */
03564       if (d->vds == 0.0) {
03565         assert(Vdseff == 0.0);
03566         assert(dVdseff_dVg == 0.0);
03567         assert(dVdseff_dVb == 0.0);
03568       }
03569       if (Vdseff > d->vds) {    // From Spice, to fix numeric problems.
03570         trace2("numeric problems", Vdseff, d->vds);
03571         Vdseff = d->vds;
03572       }
03573       trace4("fixed", Vdseff, dVdseff_dVg, dVdseff_dVd, dVdseff_dVb);
03574 
03575       diffVds = d->vds - Vdseff;
03576       trace2("", Vdseff, diffVds);
03578     }
03579     trace2("", Vdseff, diffVds);
03580     trace3("", dVdseff_dVg, dVdseff_dVd, dVdseff_dVb);
03581     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03582     /* Calculate Ids */
03583     double Idsa, dIdsa_dVg, dIdsa_dVd, dIdsa_dVb;
03584     {
03585       double Va, dVa_dVg, dVa_dVd, dVa_dVb;
03586       {
03587         /* Calculate VACLM */
03588         double VACLM, dVACLM_dVg, dVACLM_dVb, dVACLM_dVd;
03589         if ((s->pclm > 0.0) && (diffVds > 1.0e-10)) {
03590           double T0 = 1.0 / (s->pclm * Abulk * s->litl);
03591           double dT0_dVb = -T0 / Abulk * dAbulk_dVb;
03592           double dT0_dVg = -T0 / Abulk * dAbulk_dVg; 
03593           double T2 = d->vgst / EsatL;
03594           double T1 = s->leff * (Abulk + T2); 
03595           double dT1_dVg = s->leff * ((1.0-T2*dEsatL_dVg)/EsatL + dAbulk_dVg);
03596           double dT1_dVb = s->leff * (dAbulk_dVb - T2 * dEsatL_dVb / EsatL);
03597           double dT1_dVd = -T2 * dEsatL_dVd / Esat;
03598           double T9 = T0 * T1;
03599           VACLM = T9 * diffVds;
03600           dVACLM_dVg = T0 * dT1_dVg * diffVds - T9 * dVdseff_dVg
03601             + T1 * diffVds * dT0_dVg;
03602           dVACLM_dVb = (dT0_dVb*T1 + T0*dT1_dVb) * diffVds - T9 * dVdseff_dVb;
03603           dVACLM_dVd = T0 * dT1_dVd * diffVds + T9 * (1.0 - dVdseff_dVd);
03604         }else{
03605           VACLM = MAX_EXP;
03606           dVACLM_dVd = dVACLM_dVg = dVACLM_dVb = 0.0;
03607         }
03608         trace4("", VACLM, dVACLM_dVg, dVACLM_dVb, dVACLM_dVd);
03609 
03610         /* Calculate VADIBL */
03611         double VADIBL, dVADIBL_dVg, dVADIBL_dVb, dVADIBL_dVd;
03612         if (t->thetaRout > 0.0) {
03613           double T8 = Abulk * Vdsat;
03614           double T0 = Vgst2Vtm * T8;
03615           double dT0_dVg = Vgst2Vtm * Abulk * dVdsat_dVg + T8
03616             + Vgst2Vtm * Vdsat * dAbulk_dVg;
03617           double dT0_dVb = Vgst2Vtm * (dAbulk_dVb*Vdsat + Abulk*dVdsat_dVb);
03618           double dT0_dVd = Vgst2Vtm * Abulk * dVdsat_dVd;
03619           double T1 = Vgst2Vtm + T8;
03620           double dT1_dVg = 1.0 + Abulk * dVdsat_dVg + Vdsat * dAbulk_dVg;
03621           double dT1_dVb = Abulk * dVdsat_dVb + dAbulk_dVb * Vdsat;
03622           double dT1_dVd = Abulk * dVdsat_dVd;
03623           double T9 = T1 * T1;
03624           double T2 = t->thetaRout;
03625           VADIBL = (Vgst2Vtm - T0 / T1) / T2;
03626           dVADIBL_dVg = (1.0 - dT0_dVg / T1 + T0 * dT1_dVg / T9) / T2;
03627           dVADIBL_dVb = (-dT0_dVb / T1 + T0 * dT1_dVb / T9) / T2;
03628           dVADIBL_dVd = (-dT0_dVd / T1 + T0 * dT1_dVd / T9) / T2;
03629           
03630           double T7 = s->pdiblb * Vbseff;
03631           if (T7 >= -0.9) {
03632             double T3 = 1.0 / (1.0 + T7);
03633             VADIBL *= T3;
03634             dVADIBL_dVg *= T3;
03635             dVADIBL_dVb = (dVADIBL_dVb - VADIBL * s->pdiblb) * T3;
03636             dVADIBL_dVd *= T3;
03637           }else{
03638             /* Added to avoid the discontinuity problem caused by pdiblcb */
03639             double T4 = 1.0 / (0.8 + T7);
03640             double T3 = (17.0 + 20.0 * T7) * T4;
03641             dVADIBL_dVg *= T3;
03642             dVADIBL_dVb = dVADIBL_dVb * T3 - VADIBL * s->pdiblb * T4 * T4;
03643             dVADIBL_dVd *= T3;
03644             VADIBL *= T3;
03645           }
03646         }else{
03647           VADIBL = MAX_EXP;
03648           dVADIBL_dVd = dVADIBL_dVg = dVADIBL_dVb = 0.0;
03649         }
03650         trace4("", VADIBL, dVADIBL_dVg, dVADIBL_dVb, dVADIBL_dVd);
03651 
03652         /* Calculate VA */
03653         double T8 = s->pvag / EsatL;
03654         double T9 = T8 * d->vgst;
03655         double T0, dT0_dVg, dT0_dVb, dT0_dVd;
03656         if (T9 > -0.9) {
03657           T0 = 1.0 + T9;
03658           dT0_dVg = T8 * (1.0 - d->vgst * dEsatL_dVg / EsatL);
03659           dT0_dVb = -T9 * dEsatL_dVb / EsatL;
03660           dT0_dVd = -T9 * dEsatL_dVd / EsatL;
03661         }else{
03662           /* Added to avoid the discontinuity problems caused by pvag */
03663           double T1 = 1.0 / (17.0 + 20.0 * T9);
03664           T0 = (0.8 + T9) * T1;
03665           T1 *= T1;
03666           dT0_dVg = T8 * (1.0 - d->vgst * dEsatL_dVg / EsatL) * T1;
03667           T9 *= T1 / EsatL;
03668           dT0_dVb = -T9 * dEsatL_dVb;
03669           dT0_dVd = -T9 * dEsatL_dVd;
03670         }
03671         double tmp1 = VACLM * VACLM;
03672         double tmp2 = VADIBL * VADIBL;
03673         double tmp3 = VACLM + VADIBL;
03674         
03675         double T1 = VACLM * VADIBL / tmp3;
03676         tmp3 *= tmp3;
03677         double dT1_dVg = (tmp1 * dVADIBL_dVg + tmp2 * dVACLM_dVg) / tmp3;
03678         double dT1_dVd = (tmp1 * dVADIBL_dVd + tmp2 * dVACLM_dVd) / tmp3;
03679         double dT1_dVb = (tmp1 * dVADIBL_dVb + tmp2 * dVACLM_dVb) / tmp3;
03680         
03681         Va = Vasat + T0 * T1;
03682         dVa_dVg = dVasat_dVg + T1 * dT0_dVg + T0 * dT1_dVg;
03683         dVa_dVd = dVasat_dVd + T1 * dT0_dVd + T0 * dT1_dVd;
03684         dVa_dVb = dVasat_dVb + T1 * dT0_dVb + T0 * dT1_dVb;
03685       }
03686       trace4("", Va, dVa_dVg, dVa_dVd, dVa_dVb);
03687 
03688       double Idl, dIdl_dVg, dIdl_dVd, dIdl_dVb;
03689       {
03690         double gche, dgche_dVg, dgche_dVd, dgche_dVb;
03691         {
03692           double beta, dbeta_dVg, dbeta_dVd, dbeta_dVb;
03693           {
03694             double CoxWovL = m->cox * Weff / s->leff;
03695             beta = ueff * CoxWovL;
03696             dbeta_dVg = CoxWovL * dueff_dVg + beta * dWeff_dVg / Weff;
03697             dbeta_dVd = CoxWovL * dueff_dVd;
03698             dbeta_dVb = CoxWovL * dueff_dVb + beta * dWeff_dVb / Weff;
03699           }
03700           trace4("", beta, dbeta_dVg, dbeta_dVd, dbeta_dVb);
03701 
03702           double fgche1, dfgche1_dVg, dfgche1_dVd, dfgche1_dVb;
03703           {
03704             double T0 = 1.0 - 0.5 * Abulk * Vdseff / Vgst2Vtm;
03705             double dT0_dVg = -0.5 * (Abulk * dVdseff_dVg 
03706                 - Abulk * Vdseff / Vgst2Vtm + Vdseff * dAbulk_dVg) / Vgst2Vtm;
03707             double dT0_dVd = -0.5 * Abulk * dVdseff_dVd / Vgst2Vtm;
03708             double dT0_dVb = -0.5 * (Abulk*dVdseff_dVb + dAbulk_dVb*Vdseff) 
03709               / Vgst2Vtm;
03710             fgche1 = d->vgst * T0;
03711             dfgche1_dVg = d->vgst * dT0_dVg + T0; 
03712             dfgche1_dVd = d->vgst * dT0_dVd; 
03713             dfgche1_dVb = d->vgst * dT0_dVb; 
03714           }
03715           trace4("", fgche1, dfgche1_dVg, dfgche1_dVd, dfgche1_dVb);
03716 
03717           double fgche2, dfgche2_dVg, dfgche2_dVd, dfgche2_dVb;
03718           {
03719             double T9 = Vdseff / EsatL;
03720             fgche2 = 1.0 + T9;
03721             dfgche2_dVg = (dVdseff_dVg - T9 * dEsatL_dVg) / EsatL;
03722             dfgche2_dVd = (dVdseff_dVd - T9 * dEsatL_dVd) / EsatL;
03723             dfgche2_dVb = (dVdseff_dVb - T9 * dEsatL_dVb) / EsatL;
03724           }
03725           trace4("", fgche2, dfgche2_dVg, dfgche2_dVd, dfgche2_dVb);
03726 
03727           gche = beta * fgche1 / fgche2;
03728           dgche_dVg = (beta * dfgche1_dVg + fgche1 * dbeta_dVg
03729                        - gche * dfgche2_dVg) / fgche2;
03730           dgche_dVd = (beta * dfgche1_dVd + fgche1 * dbeta_dVd
03731                        - gche * dfgche2_dVd) / fgche2;
03732           dgche_dVb = (beta * dfgche1_dVb + fgche1 * dbeta_dVb
03733                        - gche * dfgche2_dVb) / fgche2;
03734         }
03735         trace4("", gche, dgche_dVg, dgche_dVd, dgche_dVb);
03736 
03737         double T0 = 1.0 + gche * Rds;
03738         double T9 = Vdseff / T0;
03739         Idl = gche * T9;
03740         dIdl_dVg = (gche * dVdseff_dVg + T9 * dgche_dVg) / T0
03741           - Idl * gche / T0 * dRds_dVg; 
03742         dIdl_dVd = (gche * dVdseff_dVd + T9 * dgche_dVd) / T0; 
03743         dIdl_dVb = (gche*dVdseff_dVb + T9*dgche_dVb - Idl*dRds_dVb*gche) / T0; 
03744       }
03745       trace4("", Idl, dIdl_dVg, dIdl_dVd, dIdl_dVb);
03746 
03747       double T9 =  diffVds / Va;
03748       double T0 =  1.0 + T9;
03749       Idsa = Idl * T0;
03750       dIdsa_dVg = T0 * dIdl_dVg - Idl * (dVdseff_dVg + T9 * dVa_dVg) / Va;
03751       dIdsa_dVd = T0 * dIdl_dVd + Idl * (1.0 - dVdseff_dVd - T9*dVa_dVd) / Va;
03752       dIdsa_dVb = T0 * dIdl_dVb - Idl * (dVdseff_dVb + T9 * dVa_dVb) / Va;
03753     }
03754     trace4("", Idsa, dIdsa_dVg, dIdsa_dVd, dIdsa_dVb);
03755     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03756     // d->ids, d->gds, d->gmf, d->gmbf
03757     {
03758       double VASCBE, dVASCBE_dVg, dVASCBE_dVd, dVASCBE_dVb;
03759       if (s->pscbe2 > 0.0) {
03760         if (diffVds > s->pscbe1 * s->litl / EXP_THRESHOLD) {
03761           double T0 =  s->pscbe1 * s->litl / diffVds;
03762           VASCBE = s->leff * exp(T0) / s->pscbe2;
03763           double T1 = T0 * VASCBE / diffVds;
03764           dVASCBE_dVg = T1 * dVdseff_dVg;
03765           dVASCBE_dVd = -T1 * (1.0 - dVdseff_dVd);
03766           dVASCBE_dVb = T1 * dVdseff_dVb;
03767         }else{
03768           VASCBE = MAX_EXP * s->leff/s->pscbe2;
03769           dVASCBE_dVg = dVASCBE_dVd = dVASCBE_dVb = 0.0;
03770         }
03771       }else{
03772         VASCBE = MAX_EXP;
03773         dVASCBE_dVg = dVASCBE_dVd = dVASCBE_dVb = 0.0;
03774       }
03775       double T9 = diffVds / VASCBE;
03776       double T0 = 1.0 + T9;
03777       double Ids = Idsa * T0;
03778       double Gm = T0*dIdsa_dVg - Idsa*(dVdseff_dVg + T9*dVASCBE_dVg) / VASCBE;
03779       double Gds = T0 * dIdsa_dVd 
03780         + Idsa * (1.0 - dVdseff_dVd - T9 * dVASCBE_dVd) / VASCBE;
03781       double Gmb = T0 * dIdsa_dVb
03782         - Idsa * (dVdseff_dVb + T9 * dVASCBE_dVb) / VASCBE;
03783       trace3("", T0, dIdsa_dVb, (T0 * dIdsa_dVb));
03784       trace4("", dVdseff_dVb, T9, dVASCBE_dVb, (dVdseff_dVb + T9*dVASCBE_dVb));
03785       trace3("", Idsa, VASCBE, (Idsa*(dVdseff_dVb+T9*dVASCBE_dVb)/VASCBE));
03786 
03787       Gds += Gm * dVgsteff_dVd;
03788       Gmb += Gm * dVgsteff_dVb;
03789       Gm *= dVgsteff_dVg;
03790       Gmb *= dVbseff_dVb;
03791       trace4("", Ids, Gm, Gds, Gmb);
03792       trace0("=========================");
03793 
03794       d->gds = Gds;
03795       if (d->reversed) {
03796         d->ids  = -Ids;
03797         d->gmr  = Gm;
03798         d->gmbr = Gmb;
03799         d->gmf = d->gmbf = 0;
03800       }else{
03801         d->ids  = Ids;
03802         d->gmf  = Gm;
03803         d->gmbf = Gmb;
03804         d->gmr = d->gmbr = 0.;
03805       }
03806     }
03807     trace4("", d->ids, d->gds, d->gmf, d->gmbf);
03808     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
03809     // d->isub, d->gbbs, d->gbgs, d->gbds
03810     {
03811       /* calculate substrate current Isub */
03812       double Isub, Gbd, Gbb, Gbg;
03813       double tmp = s->alpha0 + s->alpha1 * s->leff;
03814       if ((tmp <= 0.0) || (s->beta0 <= 0.0)) {
03815         Isub = Gbd = Gbb = Gbg = 0.0;
03816         trace4("no-isub", Isub, Gbd, Gbb, Gbg);
03817       }else{
03818         double T2 = tmp / s->leff;
03819         double T1, dT1_dVg, dT1_dVd, dT1_dVb;
03820         if (diffVds > s->beta0 / EXP_THRESHOLD) {
03821           double T0 = -s->beta0 / diffVds;
03822           T1 = T2 * diffVds * exp(T0);
03823           double T3 = T1 / diffVds * (T0 - 1.0);
03824           trace3("", T0, T2, T3);

03826           dT1_dVd = T3 * (dVdseff_dVd - 1.0);
03827           dT1_dVb = T3 * dVdseff_dVb;
03828           trace4("vds > ?", T1, dT1_dVg, dT1_dVd, dT1_dVb);
03829         }else{
03830           double T3 = T2 * MIN_EXP;
03831           trace2("", T2, T3);
03832           T1 = T3 * diffVds;
03833           dT1_dVg = -T3 * dVdseff_dVg;
03834           dT1_dVd = T3 * (1.0 - dVdseff_dVd);
03835           dT1_dVb = -T3 * dVdseff_dVb;
03836           trace4("vds < ?", T1, dT1_dVg, dT1_dVd, dT1_dVb);
03837         }
03838         Isub = T1 * Idsa;
03839         Gbg = T1 * dIdsa_dVg + Idsa * dT1_dVg;
03840         Gbd = T1 * dIdsa_dVd + Idsa * dT1_dVd;
03841         Gbb = T1 * dIdsa_dVb + Idsa * dT1_dVb;
03842         trace4("raw", Isub, Gbd, Gbb, Gbg);
03843         
03844         Gbd += Gbg * dVgsteff_dVd;
03845         Gbb += Gbg * dVgsteff_dVb;
03846         Gbg *= dVgsteff_dVg;
03847         Gbb *= dVbseff_dVb; /* bug fixing */
03848       }
03849       trace4("", Isub, Gbd, Gbb, Gbg);
03850       if (!(d->reversed)) {
03851         d->idb   = Isub;
03852         d->gdbds = Gbd;
03853         d->gdbgs = Gbg;
03854         d->gdbbs = Gbb;
03855         d->isb = d->gsbsd = d->gsbgd = d->gsbbd = 0.;
03856       }else{
03857         d->idb = d->gdbds = d->gdbgs = d->gdbbs = 0.;
03858         d->isb   = Isub;
03859         d->gsbsd = Gbd;
03860         d->gsbgd = Gbg;
03861         d->gsbbd = Gbb;
03862       }
03863       //double d__csub = Isub - (Gbb * Vbseff + Gbd * d->vds + Gbg * d->vgs);
03864     }
03865     trace4("", d->isub, d->gbbs, d->gbgs, d->gbds);
03866     // - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

04561           }
04562           trace3("", Cgg1, Cgd1, Cgb1);
04563           trace3("", Cbg1, Cbd1, Cbb1);
04564           trace2("2-1", d->qgate, d->qbulk);
04565           
04566           double Csg, Csd, Csb;
04567           trace1("", m->xpart);
04568           if (m->xpart > 0.5) {
04569             trace0("0/100 Charge petition model");
04570             T1 = T1 + T1;
04571             qsrc = -CoxWL * (0.5 * Vgsteff + 0.25 * T0 - T0 * T0 / T1);
04572             double T7 = (4.0 * Vgsteff - T0) / (T1 * T1);
04573             double T4 = -(0.5 + 24.0 * T0 * T0 / (T1 * T1));
04574             double T5 = -(0.25 * AbulkCV - 12.0 * AbulkCV * T0 * T7);
04575             double T6 = -(0.25 * VdseffCV - 12.0 * T0 * VdseffCV * T7);
04576             Csg = CoxWL * (T4 + T5 * dVdseffCV_dVg);
04577             Csd = CoxWL * T5 * dVdseffCV_dVd + Csg * dVgsteff_dVd;
04578             Csb = CoxWL * (T5 * dVdseffCV_dVb + T6 * dAbulkCV_dVb) 
04579               + Csg * dVgsteff_dVb;
04580             Csg *= dVgsteff_dVg;
04581           }else if (m->xpart < 0.5) {
04582             trace0("40/60 Charge petition model");
04583             T1 = T1 / 12.0;
04584             double T2 = 0.5 * CoxWL / (T1 * T1);
04585             double T3 = Vgsteff * (2.0 * T0 * T0 / 3.0 + Vgsteff
04586                                    * (Vgsteff - 4.0 * T0 / 3.0))
04587               - 2.0 * T0 * T0 * T0 / 15.0;
04588             qsrc = -T2 * T3;
04589             double T7 = 4.0 / 3.0 * Vgsteff * (Vgsteff - T0) + 0.4 * T0 * T0;
04590             double T4 = -2.0 * qsrc / T1 
04591               - T2 * (Vgsteff * (3.0 * Vgsteff - 8.0 * T0 / 3.0)
04592                       + 2.0 * T0 * T0 / 3.0);
04593             double T5 = (qsrc / T1 + T2 * T7) * AbulkCV;
04594             double T6 = (qsrc / T1 * VdseffCV + T2 * T7 * VdseffCV);
04595             Csg = (T4 + T5 * dVdseffCV_dVg);
04596             Csd = T5 * dVdseffCV_dVd + Csg * dVgsteff_dVd;
04597             Csb = (T5 * dVdseffCV_dVb + T6 * dAbulkCV_dVb) 
04598               + Csg * dVgsteff_dVb;
04599             Csg *= dVgsteff_dVg;
04600           }else{
04601             trace0("50/50 Charge petition model");
04602             qsrc = -0.5 * (d->qgate + d->qbulk);
04603             Csg = -0.5 * (Cgg1 + Cbg1);
04604             Csb = -0.5 * (Cgb1 + Cbb1); 
04605             Csd = -0.5 * (Cgd1 + Cbd1); 
04606           }
04607           trace4("", Csg, Csd, Csb, qsrc);
04608 
04609           d->qgate += Qac0 + Qsub0;
04610           d->qbulk -= (Qac0 + Qsub0);
04611           d->qdrn = -(d->qgate + d->qbulk + qsrc);
04612           trace3("2-2", d->qgate, d->qbulk, d->qdrn);
04613           
04614           double Cgg = dQac0_dVg + dQsub0_dVg + Cgg1;
04615           //double Cgd = dQac0_dVd + dQsub0_dVd + Cgd1;
04616           double Cgd = dQsub0_dVd + Cgd1;
04617           double Cgb = dQac0_dVb + dQsub0_dVb + Cgb1;
04618           trace3("", Cgg, Cgd, Cgb);
04619           
04620           double Cbg = Cbg1 - dQac0_dVg - dQsub0_dVg;
04621           //double Cbd = Cbd1 - dQac0_dVd - dQsub0_dVd;
04622           double Cbd = Cbd1 - dQsub0_dVd;
04623           double Cbb = Cbb1 - dQac0_dVb - dQsub0_dVb;
04624           trace3("", Cbg, Cbd, Cbb);
04625 
04626           Cgb *= dVbseff_dVb;
04627           Cbb *= dVbseff_dVb;
04628           Csb *= dVbseff_dVb;
04629           trace3("adjusted", Cgb, Cbb, Csb);
04630           
04631           d->cggb = Cgg;
04632           d->cgsb = -(Cgg + Cgd + Cgb);
04633           d->cgdb = Cgd;
04634           d->cdgb = -(Cgg + Cbg + Csg);
04635           d->cdsb = (Cgg + Cgd + Cgb + Cbg + Cbd + Cbb + Csg + Csd + Csb);
04636           d->cddb = -(Cgd + Cbd + Csd);
04637           d->cbgb = Cbg;
04638           d->cbsb = -(Cbg + Cbd + Cbb);
04639           d->cbdb = Cbd;
04640           trace0("end capMod == 2");
04641           assert(d->qbulk == d->qbulk);
04642           assert(d->qdrn == d->qdrn);
04643           assert(d->qgate == d->qgate);
04644         }else if (m->capMod == 3) {
04645           trace0("begin capMod == 3");
04646           double Vfbeff, dVfbeff_dVg, dVfbeff_dVb;
04647           {
04648             const double DELTA_3 = 0.02;
04649             double V3 = t->vfbzb - Vgs_eff + VbseffCV - DELTA_3;
04650             double T0;
04651             if (t->vfbzb <= 0.0) {
04652               T0 = sqrt(V3 * V3 - 4.0 * DELTA_3 * t->vfbzb);
04653               //T2 = -DELTA_3 / T0;
04654             }else{
04655               T0 = sqrt(V3 * V3 + 4.0 * DELTA_3 * t->vfbzb);
04656               //T2 = DELTA_3 / T0;
04657             }
04658             double T1 = 0.5 * (1.0 + V3 / T0);
04659             Vfbeff = t->vfbzb - 0.5 * (V3 + T0);
04660             dVfbeff_dVg = T1 * dVgs_eff_dVg;
04661             dVfbeff_dVb = -T1 * dVbseffCV_dVb;
04662           }
04663           double Cox = m->cox;
04664           double Tox = 1.0e8 * m->tox;
04665           trace2("", Cox, Tox);
04666 
04667           double Qac0, dQac0_dVg, dQac0_dVb;
04668           double Qsub0, dQsub0_dVg, dQsub0_dVd, dQsub0_dVb;
04669           {
04670             double Coxeff, dCoxeff_dVg, dCoxeff_dVb, CoxWLcen;
04671             {
04672               double Tcen, dTcen_dVg, dTcen_dVb;
04673               {
04674                 double T0 = (Vgs_eff - VbseffCV - t->vfbzb) / Tox;
04675                 double tmp = T0 * s->acde;
04676                 trace2("", T0, tmp);
04677                 if ((-EXP_THRESHOLD < tmp) && (tmp < EXP_THRESHOLD)) {
04678                   double dT0_dVg = dVgs_eff_dVg / Tox;
04679                   double dT0_dVb = -dVbseffCV_dVb / Tox;
04680                   trace4("", dT0_dVg, dT0_dVb, s->ldeb, exp(tmp));
04681                   Tcen = s->ldeb * exp(tmp);
04682                   dTcen_dVg = s->acde * Tcen;
04683                   dTcen_dVb = dTcen_dVg * dT0_dVb;
04684                   dTcen_dVg *= dT0_dVg;
04685                 }else if (tmp <= -EXP_THRESHOLD) {
04686                   Tcen = s->ldeb * MIN_EXP;
04687                   dTcen_dVg = dTcen_dVb = 0.0;
04688                 }else{
04689                   Tcen = s->ldeb * MAX_EXP;
04690                   dTcen_dVg = dTcen_dVb = 0.0;
04691                 }
04692                 trace3("1", Tcen, dTcen_dVg, dTcen_dVb);
04693                 double LINK = 1.0e-3 * m->tox;
04694                 double V3 = s->ldeb - Tcen - LINK;
04695                 double V4 = sqrt(V3 * V3 + 4.0 * LINK * s->ldeb);
04696                 double T1 = 0.5 * (1.0 + V3 / V4);
04697                 trace4("", LINK, V3, V4, T1);
04698                 Tcen = s->ldeb - 0.5 * (V3 + V4);
04699                 dTcen_dVg *= T1;
04700                 dTcen_dVb *= T1;
04701               }
04702               trace3("2", Tcen, dTcen_dVg, dTcen_dVb);
04703               {
04704                 double Ccen = P_EPS_SI / Tcen;
04705                 double T2 = Cox / (Cox + Ccen);
04706                 double T3 = -Ccen / Tcen;
04707                 trace3("Coxeff", Ccen, T2, T3);
04708                 Coxeff = T2 * Ccen;
04709                 dCoxeff_dVg = T2 * T2 * T3;
04710                 dCoxeff_dVb = dCoxeff_dVg * dTcen_dVb;
04711                 dCoxeff_dVg *= dTcen_dVg;
04712                 CoxWLcen = CoxWL * Coxeff / Cox;
04713               }
04714             }
04715             trace4("", Coxeff, dCoxeff_dVg, dCoxeff_dVb, CoxWLcen);
04716             //double Qac0, dQac0_dVg, dQac0_dVb;
04717             {
04718               trace4("Qac0", CoxWLcen, Vfbeff, t->vfbzb, Coxeff);
04719               Qac0 = CoxWLcen * (Vfbeff - t->vfbzb);
04720               double QovCox = Qac0 / Coxeff;
04721               dQac0_dVg = CoxWLcen * dVfbeff_dVg + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVg;
04722               dQac0_dVb = CoxWLcen * dVfbeff_dVb + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVb;
04723             }
04724             trace3("", Qac0, dQac0_dVg, dQac0_dVb);
04725             
04726             //double Qsub0, dQsub0_dVg, dQsub0_dVd, dQsub0_dVb;
04727             {
04728               double T0 = 0.5 * t->k1ox;
04729               double T3 = Vgs_eff - Vfbeff - VbseffCV - Vgsteff;
04730               double T1, T2;
04731               if (t->k1ox == 0.0) {
04732                 T1 = 0.0;
04733                 T2 = 0.0;
04734               }else if (T3 < 0.0) {
04735                 T1 = T0 + T3 / t->k1ox;
04736                 T2 = CoxWLcen;
04737               }else{
04738                 T1 = sqrt(T0 * T0 + T3);
04739                 T2 = CoxWLcen * T0 / T1;
04740               }
04741               
04742               Qsub0 = CoxWLcen * t->k1ox * (T1 - T0);
04743               double QovCox = Qsub0 / Coxeff;
04744               dQsub0_dVg = T2 * (dVgs_eff_dVg - dVfbeff_dVg - dVgsteff_dVg)
04745                 + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVg;
04746               dQsub0_dVd = -T2 * dVgsteff_dVd;
04747               dQsub0_dVb = -T2 * (dVfbeff_dVb + dVbseffCV_dVb + dVgsteff_dVb)
04748                 + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVb;
04749             }
04750             trace4("", Qsub0, dQsub0_dVg, dQsub0_dVd, dQsub0_dVb);
04751           } // end scope Coxeff, CoxWLcen
04752           assert(Qac0 == Qac0);
04753           assert(Qsub0 == Qsub0);
04754           
04755           double VgDP, dVgDP_dVg;
04756           {
04757             double DeltaPhi, dDeltaPhi_dVg;
04758             { /* Gate-bias dependent delta Phis begins */
04759               double Denomi, T0;
04760               if (t->k1ox <= 0.0) {
04761                 Denomi = 0.25 * s->moin * t->vtm;
04762                 T0 = 0.5 * t->sqrtPhi;
04763               }else{
04764                 Denomi = s->moin * t->vtm * t->k1ox * t->k1ox;
04765                 T0 = t->k1ox * t->sqrtPhi;
04766               }
04767               double T1 = 2.0 * T0 + Vgsteff;
04768               DeltaPhi = t->vtm * log(1.0 + T1 * Vgsteff / Denomi);
04769               dDeltaPhi_dVg = 2.0 * t->vtm * (T1-T0) / (Denomi + T1 * Vgsteff);
04770             }
04771             
04772             /* VgDP = Vgsteff - DeltaPhi */
04773             double T0 = Vgsteff - DeltaPhi - 0.001;
04774             double dT0_dVg = 1.0 - dDeltaPhi_dVg;
04775             double T1 = sqrt(T0 * T0 + Vgsteff * 0.004);
04776             VgDP = 0.5 * (T0 + T1);
04777             dVgDP_dVg = 0.5 * (dT0_dVg + (T0 * dT0_dVg + 0.002) / T1);
04778           }
04779 
04780           double Coxeff, dCoxeff_dVg, dCoxeff_dVd, dCoxeff_dVb;
04781           {
04782             double Tcen, dTcen_dVg, dTcen_dVd, dTcen_dVb;
04783             {
04784               double T3 = 4.0 * (d->von - t->vfbzb - t->phi);
04785               Tox += Tox;
04786               double T0, dT0_dVd, dT0_dVb;
04787               if (T3 >= 0.0) {
04788                 T0 = (Vgsteff + T3) / Tox;
04789                 dT0_dVd = (dVgsteff_dVd + 4.0 * dVth_dVd) / Tox;
04790                 dT0_dVb = (dVgsteff_dVb + 4.0 * dVth_dVb) / Tox;
04791               }else{
04792                 T0 = (Vgsteff + 1.0e-20) / Tox;
04793                 dT0_dVd = dVgsteff_dVd / Tox;
04794                 dT0_dVb = dVgsteff_dVb / Tox;
04795               }
04796               double tmp = exp(0.7 * log(T0));
04797               double T1 = 1.0 + tmp;
04798               double T2 = 0.7 * tmp / (T0 * Tox);
04799               Tcen = 1.9e-9 / T1;
04800               dTcen_dVg = -1.9e-9 * T2 / T1 /T1;
04801               dTcen_dVd = Tox * dTcen_dVg;
04802               dTcen_dVb = dTcen_dVd * dT0_dVb;
04803               dTcen_dVd *= dT0_dVd;
04804               dTcen_dVg *= dVgsteff_dVg;
04805             }
04806             double Ccen = P_EPS_SI / Tcen;
04807             double T0 = Cox / (Cox + Ccen);
04808             Coxeff = T0 * Ccen;
04809             double T1 = -Ccen / Tcen;
04810             dCoxeff_dVg = T0 * T0 * T1;
04811             dCoxeff_dVd = dCoxeff_dVg * dTcen_dVd;
04812             dCoxeff_dVb = dCoxeff_dVg * dTcen_dVb;
04813             dCoxeff_dVg *= dTcen_dVg;
04814           }
04815           double CoxWLcen = CoxWL * Coxeff / Cox;
04816           double AbulkCV = Abulk0 * s->abulkCVfactor;
04817           double dAbulkCV_dVb = s->abulkCVfactor * dAbulk0_dVb;
04818 
04819           double VdseffCV, dVdseffCV_dVg, dVdseffCV_dVd, dVdseffCV_dVb;
04820           {
04821             const double DELTA_4 = 0.02;
04822             double VdsatCV =  VgDP / AbulkCV;
04823             double T0 = VdsatCV - d->vds - DELTA_4;
04824             double dT0_dVg = dVgDP_dVg / AbulkCV;
04825             double dT0_dVb = -VdsatCV * dAbulkCV_dVb / AbulkCV;
04826             double T1 = sqrt(T0 * T0 + 4.0 * DELTA_4 * VdsatCV);
04827             double dT1_dVg = (T0 + DELTA_4 + DELTA_4) / T1;
04828             double dT1_dVd = -T0 / T1;
04829             double dT1_dVb = dT1_dVg * dT0_dVb;
04830             dT1_dVg *= dT0_dVg;
04831             if (T0 >= 0.0) {
04832               VdseffCV = VdsatCV - 0.5 * (T0 + T1);
04833               dVdseffCV_dVg = 0.5 * (dT0_dVg - dT1_dVg);
04834               dVdseffCV_dVd = 0.5 * (1.0 - dT1_dVd);
04835               dVdseffCV_dVb = 0.5 * (dT0_dVb - dT1_dVb);
04836             }else{
04837               double T3 = (DELTA_4 + DELTA_4) / (T1 - T0);
04838               double T4 = 1.0 - T3;
04839               double T5 = VdsatCV * T3 / (T1 - T0);
04840               VdseffCV = VdsatCV * T4;
04841               dVdseffCV_dVg = dT0_dVg * T4 + T5 * (dT1_dVg - dT0_dVg);
04842               dVdseffCV_dVd = T5 * (dT1_dVd + 1.0);
04843               dVdseffCV_dVb = dT0_dVb * (1.0 - T5) + T5 * dT1_dVb;
04844             }
04845             /* Added to eliminate non-zero VdseffCV at Vds=0.0 */
04846             if (d->vds == 0.0) {
04847               VdseffCV = 0.0;
04848               dVdseffCV_dVg = 0.0;
04849               dVdseffCV_dVb = 0.0;
04850             }
04851           }
04852           
04853           double T0 = AbulkCV * VdseffCV;
04854           double T1 = VgDP;
04855           double T2 = 12.0 * (T1 - 0.5 * T0 + 1.0e-20);
04856           double T3 = T0 / T2;
04857           double T4 = 1.0 - 12.0 * T3 * T3;
04858           double T5 = AbulkCV * (6.0 * T0 * (4.0 * T1 - T0) / (T2*T2) - 0.5);
04859           double T6 = T5 * VdseffCV / AbulkCV;
04860           d->qgate = CoxWLcen * (T1 - T0 * (0.5 - T3));
04862           
04863           double Cgg1, Cgd1, Cgb1;
04864           {
04865             double QovCox = d->qgate / Coxeff;
04866             Cgg1 = CoxWLcen * (T4 * dVgDP_dVg + T5 * dVdseffCV_dVg);
04867             Cgd1 = CoxWLcen * T5 * dVdseffCV_dVd + Cgg1 
04868               * dVgsteff_dVd + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVd;
04869             Cgb1 = CoxWLcen * (T5 * dVdseffCV_dVb + T6 * dAbulkCV_dVb) 
04870               + Cgg1 * dVgsteff_dVb + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVb;
04871             Cgg1 = Cgg1 * dVgsteff_dVg + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVg;
04872           }
04873           
04874           double T7 = 1.0 - AbulkCV;
04875           double T8 = T2 * T2;
04876           double T9 = 12.0 * T7 * T0 * T0 / (T8 * AbulkCV);
04877           double T10 = T9 * dVgDP_dVg;
04878           double T11 = -T7 * T5 / AbulkCV;
04879           double T12 = -(T9 * T1 / AbulkCV + VdseffCV * (0.5 - T0 / T2));
04880           d->qbulk = CoxWLcen * T7 * (0.5 * VdseffCV - T0 * VdseffCV / T2);
04881 
04882           assert(d->qbulk == d->qbulk);
04883           assert(d->qdrn == d->qdrn);
04884           assert(d->qgate == d->qgate);
04885           
04886           double Cbg1, Cbd1, Cbb1;
04887           {
04888             double QovCox = d->qbulk / Coxeff;
04889             Cbg1 = CoxWLcen * (T10 + T11 * dVdseffCV_dVg);
04890             Cbd1 = CoxWLcen * T11 * dVdseffCV_dVd + Cbg1
04891               * dVgsteff_dVd + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVd; 
04892             Cbb1 = CoxWLcen * (T11 * dVdseffCV_dVb + T12 * dAbulkCV_dVb)
04893               + Cbg1 * dVgsteff_dVb + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVb;
04894             Cbg1 = Cbg1 * dVgsteff_dVg + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVg;
04895           }
04897           double Csg, Csd, Csb;
04898           if (m->xpart > 0.5) {
04899             /* 0/100 partition */
04900             qsrc = -CoxWLcen * (T1 / 2.0 + T0 / 4.0 - 0.5 * T0 * T0 / T2);
04901             double QovCox = qsrc / Coxeff;
04902             T2 += T2;
04903             T3 = T2 * T2;
04904             T7 = -(0.25 - 12.0 * T0 * (4.0 * T1 - T0) / T3);
04905             T4 = -(0.5 + 24.0 * T0 * T0 / T3) * dVgDP_dVg;
04906             T5 = T7 * AbulkCV;
04907             T6 = T7 * VdseffCV;
04908             
04909             Csg = CoxWLcen * (T4 + T5 * dVdseffCV_dVg);
04910             Csd = CoxWLcen * T5 * dVdseffCV_dVd + Csg * dVgsteff_dVd
04911               + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVd;
04912             Csb = CoxWLcen * (T5 * dVdseffCV_dVb + T6 * dAbulkCV_dVb)
04913               + Csg * dVgsteff_dVb + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVb;
04914             Csg = Csg * dVgsteff_dVg + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVg;
04915           }else if (m->xpart < 0.5) {
04916             /* 40/60 partition */
04917             T2 = T2 / 12.0;
04918             T3 = 0.5 * CoxWLcen / (T2 * T2);
04919             T4 = T1 * (2.0 * T0 * T0 / 3.0 + T1 * (T1 - 4.0 * T0 / 3.0))
04920               - 2.0 * T0 * T0 * T0 / 15.0;
04921             qsrc = -T3 * T4;
04922             double QovCox = qsrc / Coxeff;
04923             T8 = 4.0 / 3.0 * T1 * (T1 - T0) + 0.4 * T0 * T0;
04924             T5 = -2.0 * qsrc / T2 
04925               - T3 * (T1 * (3.0 * T1 - 8.0 * T0 / 3.0) + 2.0 * T0 * T0 / 3.0);
04926             T6 = AbulkCV * (qsrc / T2 + T3 * T8);
04927             T7 = T6 * VdseffCV / AbulkCV; 
04928             
04929             Csg = T5 * dVgDP_dVg + T6 * dVdseffCV_dVg; 
04930             Csd = Csg * dVgsteff_dVd + T6 * dVdseffCV_dVd 
04931               + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVd;
04932             Csb = Csg * dVgsteff_dVb + T6 * dVdseffCV_dVb 
04933               + T7 * dAbulkCV_dVb + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVb; 
04934             Csg = Csg * dVgsteff_dVg + QovCox * dCoxeff_dVg;
04935           }else{
04936             /* 50/50 partition */
04937             qsrc = -0.5 * d->qgate;
04938             Csg = -0.5 * Cgg1;
04939             Csd = -0.5 * Cgd1; 
04940             Csb = -0.5 * Cgb1; 
04941           }
04943           assert(Qsub0 == Qsub0);
04944           assert(Qac0 == Qac0);
04945 
04946           d->qgate += Qac0 + Qsub0 - d->qbulk;
04947           d->qbulk -= (Qac0 + Qsub0);
04948           d->qdrn = -(d->qgate + d->qbulk + qsrc);
04949 
04950           assert(d->qbulk == d->qbulk);
